{
  "name": "add-a-direct-post-mode-to-20260412-2125",
  "idea": "Add a direct post mode to share_to_social that accepts media URLs + tweet text directly, without requiring a Discord message. This is needed so we can post tweets (e.g. reply to a banodoco tweet with a video) using external media URLs (like Supabase video links) rather than needing a Discord message reference. The tool should still support scheduled_at, action (post/reply/retweet), target_post, and route_override. It should download the media from the URL to a temp file, then feed it through the existing upload/publish pipeline. Keep it minimal \u2014 don't restructure the existing message-based flow, just add an alternative entry path.",
